<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,562,1036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,462,935,961]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">General distribution:</emphasis>
An eastern species ranging from Massachusetts south to Florida, west to Louisiana and Texas, and in the Midwest from Ohio to Kansas.
</paragraph>
